latest_release.name: Version 2.1.20
latest_release.body:
- Regenerate README file [[#422](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/422)]
- Improve warning message for install and activate multiple themes [[#419](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/419)]
- Replace User Switching from feature tests [[#418](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/418)]
- Update the theme in feature tests [[#417](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/417)]
- Show additional plugin headers values in `wp plugin get <plugin>` output [[#414](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/414)]
- Add `tested_up_to` field [[#413](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/413)]
- Warn multiple themes installation with activate [[#408](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/408)]
- Regenerate README file [[#404](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/404)]
- Fix plugin commands examples [[#403](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/403)]
- Regenerate README file [[#402](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/402)]
- Update theme commands examples [[#401](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/401)]
- Correct param type in Parse Theme Name trait [[#400](https://github.com/wp-cli/extension-command/pull/400)]
